    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎加入我们的游戏讨论群</h2>官方玩家群：548253790<br>我们期望听到你的声音!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/20456fafc73883e13446172195f146ec.poster.avif?t=1740407874\" width=600 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/20456fafc73883e13446172195f146ec.webm?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/20456fafc73883e13446172195f146ec.mp4?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在枪林弹雨中突破核心！</h2><br>这是一款快节奏横版动作射击Roguelite游戏。你作为在人类被机械灭绝后被唤醒的机器人，诺瓦，需要在看守森严的地下遗迹中倚靠灵活的身手和强力的枪械，突破重重封锁直达核心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/c44a89e883113c1b197f7724dddb6947.poster.avif?t=1740407874\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/c44a89e883113c1b197f7724dddb6947.webm?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/c44a89e883113c1b197f7724dddb6947.mp4?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >行云流水的战斗！</h2><br>畅快无阻地跑、跳、冲刺、射击，灵活搭配多种近战攻击方式，射爆一切拦路的杂鱼。部分战斗可能并不如割草般容易，但通过行云流水的操作击败强敌正是爽快感的来源。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/0cd4fc3ddb4237212d763270127cfa45.poster.avif?t=1740407874\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/0cd4fc3ddb4237212d763270127cfa45.webm?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/0cd4fc3ddb4237212d763270127cfa45.mp4?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每一次死亡都是新的起点！</h2><br>无论多少次失手倒下，诺瓦都能在遗迹外被修复并再次启程。虽然进度会被重置，但在遗迹深处搜集的元件将会被保存。你可以用它升级诺瓦的系统以解锁更强的技能、更丰富的动作，抑或是更多的支援和更实用的武器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/5c77e90554af0bf8f07745cf7ef096f2.poster.avif?t=1740407874\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/5c77e90554af0bf8f07745cf7ef096f2.webm?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/5c77e90554af0bf8f07745cf7ef096f2.mp4?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >错综复杂的地下迷宫！</h2><br>地下遗迹不仅庞大，每次探索还都会改变内部构造。随着探索的深入，敌人的类型和配置也会发生变化。并且除了守护每个阶层的Boss以外，还有各种强大的精英敌人等待着你的挑战。<br>你可以打碎墙壁找到隐藏房间获取秘宝，也可以通过遗迹中散落的强化终端和武器商店来武装自己，但无需惧怕死亡，每一次启程你都会变得更强。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/a9de672b5af2db389b5c0d995fde9354.poster.avif?t=1740407874\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/a9de672b5af2db389b5c0d995fde9354.webm?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044660/extras/a9de672b5af2db389b5c0d995fde9354.mp4?t=1740407874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
